{"tid":1408414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[豬隊友]尹兆堅早前提出修訂刑事司法管轄權條例，草案獲律政司發出證明書。","createTime":"2019-08-04T17:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:59:06.000Z","uid":191740,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"74635bf7b8674b600e5afafe98e5058c9e5e1f43","tid":1408414,"uid":191740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】立法會議員尹兆堅早前提出修訂刑事司法管轄權條例，以處理台灣殺人案，草案獲律政司發出證明書，可提交上立法會。<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅的草案提出，把港人在海外干犯謀殺、誤殺和意圖謀殺等罪行納入條例的涵蓋範圍，讓香港法院有司法管轄權，審理相關案件，他呼籲立法會主席梁君彥盡快處理。<br />\n<br />\n他重申，現時社會爭議已經超出逃犯條例修訂爭議，要求政府回應市民訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=357733&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357733%26refer%3D&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHafGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=25d05dbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357733%26refer%3D&h=406277b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=357733&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"474adaffb308669181481b8a4e1d839dbee284fa","tid":1408414,"uid":179292,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"民主黨係咁水平"},{"pid":"586a772fd3f04f6f074f9c0ed01602bf4a48bd53","tid":1408414,"uid":191740,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:16:59.000Z","msg":"過左實搞散場運動，泛民變相重新賦予政府同立法會正當性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3067ba6ec826b001310e5835c8c417dc0adf17","tid":1408414,"uid":583,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"474adaffb308669181481b8a4e1d839dbee284fa","tid":1408414,"uid":179292,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"民主黨係咁水平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:17:22.000Z","msg":"又黎張超雄式分化"},{"pid":"52fa325fb38992e4f41fc44e0b6e4a910fa8a839","tid":1408414,"uid":583,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":